- If in-housing is the right option, then: 
 - auditing and selection process of the right inhousing technology, processes and system
integrations
 - comprehensive data strategy to ensure that you have the right data, are compliant with all
the legal requirements of owning and handling customer data
 - HR/talent liaison to develop job descriptions, selection process, hiring and on-boarding of
new staff into the team
 - ongoing assessment and support of
 - negotiation and trading support to ensure that you develop the right relationships with the
right media owners and technology suppliers</p>
